PrecisAppointment of CATHERINE ACZEL BOIVIE of Burnaby, British Columbia, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Foundation for Innovation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective October 29, 2018, in the place of Alain Beaudet, whose term has expired.
